title: Sinkhole at center of White House cover up
text:
Sinkhole at center of White House cover up 00:30
Groundkeepers at the White House have covered up a sinkhole on the North Lawn that has spawned jokes online about ''draining the swamp.'' Rough Cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
